"1 pound uncooked medium elbow macaroni","1 1/2 cups chopped lean ham","1 1/2 cups frozen peas","  Cooking spray","1/2 cup finely chopped onion","3 cups 2% reduced-fat milk","1 cup (4 ounces) shredded reduced-fat extrasharp cheddar cheese","1 cup (4 ounces) shredded Swiss cheese","3/4 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1/8 teaspoon ground red pepper","2  (1-ounce) slices white bread","2 tablespoons butter, melted"